creator: Amplio
descriptionHtml:
Android based Talking Book loader runs on Phones or Tablets.

Download new content in the office, then go out into the field to install it on Talking Books. When you get back to the office, statistics and user feedback will upload automatically.
descriptionShort: A highly portable Talking Book Loader.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Fixed a problem launching the app when not connected to the internet.
